data.description: MAIN-FLOOR BEDROOM | FLEX SPACE Prepare to be impressed by this BEAUTIFUL 2-story home in the Island Lakes at Midtown Community! The home boasts a flex space and a guest suite with a walk-in closet on the main floor. The kitchen features gorgeous cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances (includes refrigerator, range, microwave, and dishwasher). All other bedrooms are on the 2nd floor. The oversized primary suite has a private bath with dual vanity sinks and a walk-in closet. This desirable home also comes complete with a 2-car garage and front porch. This community offers a walking trail, close to major freeways and shopping centers.
